Package: ditto
Title: String and Text Similarity Metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Willem", "Sleegers", , "w.sleegers@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utilities for comparing strings and short texts. Includes a
    from-scratch BLEU implementation and a BERTScore metric computed from
    token-level embeddings served by a local 'llama.cpp' server, alongside a
    unified compare_strings() interface that returns edit-distance, n-gram,
    and embedding-based similarity scores in a single table.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
